SELECT 
    'ChangePurchaseDocument' || '::' || "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."ID"  AS "ID",
    "PurchaseDocument"."ID"                                              AS "PurchaseDocument",
    "PurchaseDocument"."ID"                                              AS "PurchaseOrder",
    "PurchaseDocument"."DocumentCategory"                                       AS "DocumentCategory",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."Time"                                    AS "Time",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."ChangedBy"                               AS "ExecutedBy",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."Attribute"                               AS "ChangedAttribute",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."ExecutionType"                           AS "ExecutionType",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."OldValue"                                AS "OldValue",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."NewValue"                                AS "NewValue"
FROM "o_custom_PurchaseDocument" AS "PurchaseDocument"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_PurchaseDocument" AS "PurchaseDocument_Changes"
        ON "PurchaseDocument"."ID" = "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."ObjectID"
WHERE "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."Attribute" IN ('Vendor', 'Currency', 'PaymentTerms', 'ReleaseIndicator')
    AND "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
